this afternoon at 4.

1229
01:17:52,640 --> 01:17:55,279
- We are adjourned.
- All rise.

1230
01:17:55,480 --> 01:17:56,959
All right.

1231
01:18:00,960 --> 01:18:03,030
You heard the questions.
