that you could be depended on...

1244
01:18:41,800 --> 01:18:45,270
...on Tuesdays and every other
Thursday to give a fair ruling.

1245
01:18:45,480 --> 01:18:47,630
Will you please listen to me?

1246
01:18:48,200 --> 01:18:50,919
