on this case.

1247
01:18:51,120 --> 01:18:54,192
I think the least you could do is
give me one minute of your attention.

1248
01:18:54,400 --> 01:18:55,355
It wouldn't matter.

1249
01:18:57,240 --> 01:18:59,629
I've already made my decision.

1250
01:19:00,080 --> 01:19:02,116
And even though
it's not a Tuesday...

1251
01:19:02,320 --> 01:19:06,279
...I just signed the order
releasing Calvin Willis from prison.

1252
01:19:16,000 --> 01:19:18,389
You mean, Calvin's getting out?

1253
01:19:22,400 --> 01:19:24,277
We don't wanna spoil the surprise...

1254
01:19:24,480 --> 01:19:27,074
...for old Heinz now, do we?

1255
01:19:32,480 --> 01:19:34,755
No, sir, we don't.

1256
01:19:34,960 --> 01:19:37,918
Thank you, Lord. Hallelujah.

1257
01:19:38,120 --> 01:19:39,519
Lord, you're just so good.

1258
01:19:39,720 --> 01:19:42,792
You're most kind, Lord. Lord Jesus.

1259
01:19:43,000 --> 01:19:45,719
You've just been so good.

1260
01:19:47,120 --> 01:19:49,236
Thank you, blessed Jesus.

1261
01:19:49,440 --> 01:19:51,237
- Thank you!
- Are you getting this?

1262
01:19:51,440 --> 01:19:53,396
Thank the Lord.

1263
01:19:54,920 --> 01:19:56,672
Thank you.

1264
01:19:57,320 --> 01:19:59,356
Oh, I wouldn't wanna step
without you, Lord.

1265
01:19:59,560 --> 01:20:02,028
Lord, I thank you. I thank you.

1266
01:20:02,240 --> 01:20:04,196
Thank you, Lord.

1267
01:21:16,760 --> 01:21:19,274
Your lady friend
brought these for you.

1268
01:21:19,960 --> 01:21:21,791
Get dressed.

1269
