1276
01:22:12,080 --> 01:22:14,514
You know, these white folks' clothes.

1277
01:22:15,920 --> 01:22:18,195
Yeah. I thought you wouldn't mind.

1278
01:22:18,400 --> 01:22:21,710
I bought the shirt for Randy,
but it's never been worn.

1279
01:22:25,040 --> 01:22:26,678
You know...

1280
01:22:27,520 --> 01:22:29,750
...I never known nobody like you.

1281
01:22:30,960 --> 01:22:33,952
Well, that's because
you've been inside for 20 years.

1282
01:22:36,880 --> 01:22:38,916
I just wanna say thank you.

1283
01:22:53,760 --> 01:22:56,832
I don't wanna be crying.
I don't wanna cry.

1284
01:23:00,640 --> 01:23:05,316
You know, I see
why Randy never wore these.

1285
01:23:10,720 --> 01:23:14,076
- It's dry. Ready?
- Yes, ma'am.

1286
01:23:23,320 --> 01:23:26,357
Yes, Lord. Yes, Lord.

1287
01:23:30,880 --> 01:23:32,108
Thank you, Lord.

1288
01:23:57,880 --> 01:24:00,474
It just feels wonderful. Just wonderful.

1289
01:24:00,680 --> 01:24:02,671
I've waited a long time.

